<item>
            <title>[FELIX-2824] Components that have a ConfigurationPolicy value of REQUIRE fail to activate</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-2824</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Components that have a ConfigurationPolicy value of REQUIRE are no longer configured and activated by configuration admin.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This was working fine in scr-1.6.0 and earlier versions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Felix 3.0.6&lt;br/&gt;
Config admin 1.2.8</environment>
